<br>
::She moved towards her hut and went inside, ignoring her wound and instead tumbling into bed so that she could rest, at least for a time. Such little rest she knew. Sartha barely ever slept, but would today:: <p>~The old days are gone. You can't live in the past, and you can't wait for the future. Now is all we have. You do the other two, you waste your life...
